# Office
########################################

IMAPAccount office
Host outlook.office365.com 
User cxiong001@e.ntu.edu.sg
PassCmd "gpg2 -q --pinentry-mode loopback --for-your-eyes-only --no-tty -d ~/.password/office.gpg"
AuthMechs LOGIN
SSLType IMAPS

IMAPStore office-remote
Account office

MaildirStore office-local
Path ~/Mail/office/
Inbox ~/Mail/office/inbox

Channel office
Master :office-remote:
Slave :office-local:
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *
Patterns *
